N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 76.2 - Definitions

State Regulations

As used in this Part, the following words and terms have the indicated meanings: (a) Commissioner means the State Commissioner of Health. (b) Department means the State Department of Health. (c) Person means any statutory or legal entity recognized in New York State law. Notes
